topic: Movie Workflow Series ("Horror Franchises explorative search")

goals.1: Investigate the workers of the two original movies and check any commonality
goals.2: Check who was the most famous actor/actress on Halloween and Friday the 13th at the time of the release (e.g., the actor/actress who acted in more movies before and/or the actor/actress who won more academy awards)
goals.3: Check which actor/actress did more movies after the release of these two films (consider the films separately)
goals.4: Get all the movies of the two franchises (return year and director)
goals.5: Who is most involved in a franchise (who did something in the movies, e.g., writer, director, producer)?
goals.6: Investigate which franchise is highly regarded by the critics overall
